revere the rational mind

00:02:48.200 --> 00:02:52.640 align:middle line:84%
and to analyze and to create
and to really revere A plus B

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:54.050 align:middle line:84%
equals C, that
kinds of thinking.

00:02:54.050 --> 00:02:57.710 align:middle line:84%
But intuition and seeing
comes deep from the soul.

00:02:57.710 --> 00:03:01.220 align:middle line:84%
And it's part of our legacy as
human beings to activate this.

00:03:01.220 --> 00:03:03.530 align:middle line:84%
And I think what so many
adults are doing now

00:03:03.530 --> 00:03:06.350 align:middle line:84%
