intuitive sense of connection

00:03:06.350 --> 00:03:08.363 align:middle line:84%
with the soul and the
kind of information that

00:03:08.363 --> 00:03:09.280 align:middle line:90%
could come through it.

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:11.930 align:middle line:84%
And so many people want
to really develop this

00:03:11.930 --> 00:03:14.995 align:middle line:84%
and to all those people,
I've dedicated my new book.

00:03:14.995 --> 00:03:20.570 align:middle line:84%
>> Your experience started
being an intuitive.

00:03:20.570 --> 00:03:21.710 align:middle line:90%
You are a psychic child.

00:03:21.710 --> 00:03:22.730 align:middle line:90%
>> I was.

00:03:22.730 --> 00:03:24.950 align:middle line:84%
I had many premonitions
as a child.

00:03:24.950 --> 00:03:27.890 align:middle line:84%
