physicians in my family

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.450 align:middle line:84%
so there is a lot of
linear rational thinking

00:03:32.450 --> 00:03:34.250 align:middle line:90%
in my heritage.

00:03:34.250 --> 00:03:36.830 align:middle line:84%
And I grew up making
predictions about deaths,

00:03:36.830 --> 00:03:38.360 align:middle line:90%
illnesses, earthquakes.

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:40.490 align:middle line:84%
