I predicted the suicide

00:03:40.490 --> 00:03:41.990 align:middle line:90%
of my parents' friend.

00:03:41.990 --> 00:03:44.640 align:middle line:84%
And so by about age
11, I had made so many

00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:45.890 align:middle line:90%
of these negative predictions.

00:03:45.890 --> 00:03:48.680 align:middle line:84%
My parents forbade me to ever
talk about my premonitions

00:03:48.680 --> 00:03:49.700 align:middle line:90%
again at home.

00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:52.280 align:middle line:84%
So I grew up thinking there
was something wrong with me,

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:54.303 align:middle line:84%
that I was able to somehow
cause these events,

00:03:54.303 --> 00:03:55.220 align:middle line:90%
I was able to predict.

00:03:55.220 --> 00:03:56.120 align:middle line:90%
It was so wrong.

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:58.280 align:middle line:84%
Many misconceptions
that children have.

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:00.770 align:middle line:84%
But I grew up ashamed of
my intuitive abilities

00:04:00.770 --> 00:04:03.590 align:middle line:84%
and my own healing
path has been learning

00:04:03.590 --> 00:04:05.720 align:middle line:84%
how to integrate
intuition into my being

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:10.310 align:middle line:84%
and not to censor that voice
and to be large and incorporate

00:04:10.310 --> 00:04:12.883 align:middle line:84%
linear thinking with
intuition, with being a woman,

00:04:12.883 --> 00:04:14.300 align:middle line:84%
with being a
psychiatrist, and not

00:04:14.300 --> 00:04:18.170 align:middle line:84%
splitting off any aspects of
myself but being totally whole

00:04:18.170 --> 00:04:20.480 align:middle line:84%
and totally embracing
my capacity to see

00:04:20.480 --> 00:04:23.220 align:middle line:84%
and encouraging
others to do the same.

00:04:23.220 --> 00:04:27.500 align:middle line:84%
>> It's pretty unusual speaking
of how far this type of thing

00:04:27.500 --> 00:04:31.408 align:middle line:84%
has come that the American
Psychiatric Association has

00:04:31.408 --> 00:04:33.325 align:middle line:84%
asked you to be one of
the featured speakers--

00:04:33.325 --> 00:04:34.110 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, yes.

00:04:34.110 --> 00:04:34.580 align:middle line:90%
>> --at their convention.

00:04:34.580 --> 00:04:35.830 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, it's an amazing thing.

00:04:35.830 --> 00:04:37.730 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to be speaking
about how intuition

00:04:37.730 --> 00:04:39.483 align:middle line:90%
can enhance patient care.

00:04:39.483 --> 00:04:40.900 align:middle line:84%
And this is wonderful
because it's

00:04:40.900 --> 00:04:43.340 align:middle line:84%
saying to me that traditional
psychiatry is beginning

00:04:43.340 --> 00:04:47.930 align:middle line:84%
to open up to possibilities
of intuition, of spirituality,

00:04:47.930 --> 00:04:50.392 align:middle line:84%
that they're not
just negating it,

00:04:50.392 --> 00:04:52.100 align:middle line:84%
and they're opening
their hearts to this.

00:04:52.100 --> 00:04:53.683 align:middle line:84%
And so many patients
are wanting this.

00:04:53.683 --> 00:04:55.400 align:middle line:84%
What I'm seeing all
around the country

00:04:55.400 --> 00:04:57.440 align:middle line:84%
is that patients
all over are wanting

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:00.020 align:middle line:84%
to incorporate
intuition spirituality

00:05:00.020 --> 00:05:01.597 align:middle line:90%
into traditional therapy.

00:05:01.597 --> 00:05:02.930 align:middle line:90%
That's what they're longing for.

00:05:02.930 --> 00:05:04.472 align:middle line:84%
And I think traditional
psychiatry is

00:05:04.472 --> 00:05:06.760 align:middle line:90%
beginning to respond to that.

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:10.970 align:middle line:84%
>> It's important to note for
the viewer here that this book

00:05:10.970 --> 00:05:13.330 align:middle line:84%
is not written
for psychiatrists.

00:05:13.330 --> 00:05:14.990 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, no, not at all.

00:05:14.990 --> 00:05:17.300 align:middle line:84%
>> This book is written for
the garden variety everyday

00:05:17.300 --> 00:05:17.630 align:middle line:90%
person--

00:05:17.630 --> 00:05:18.380 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:05:18.380 --> 00:05:19.180 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:05:19.180 --> 00:05:23.870 align:middle line:84%
>> --who is perhaps very
intuitive as say we all are.

00:05:23.870 --> 00:05:26.630 align:middle line:84%
>> Or not, or it's written
for someone who has never had

00:05:26.630 --> 00:05:29.960 align:middle line:84%
an intuition in their life and
is interested in developing

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:32.720 align:middle line:84%
that or was never remember
to dream in their life and is

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:35.690 align:middle line:84%
curious about what would it be
like if I had a dream and what

00:05:35.690 --> 00:05:37.010 align:middle line:90%
would my dream tell me.

00:05:37.010 --> 00:05:39.260 align:middle line:84%
I've worked with so many
people in my private practice

00:05:39.260 --> 00:05:41.585 align:middle line:84%
as a psychiatrist who swear
they're not intuitive,

00:05:41.585 --> 00:05:43.880 align:middle line:84%
who swear they haven't
been able to dream.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:45.530 align:middle line:84%
And every single
person I've been

00:05:45.530 --> 00:05:48.140 align:middle line:84%
able to teach to tune
into their intuition.

00:05:48.140 --> 00:05:51.647 align:middle line:84%
But tuning into intuition is
one thing, that's the easy part.

00:05:51.647 --> 00:05:53.480 align:middle line:84%
But getting people to
act on their intuition

00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:54.230 align:middle line:90%
is another thing.

00:05:54.230 --> 00:05:55.313 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS] >> That's harder.

00:05:55.313 --> 00:05:57.820 align:middle line:84%
>> But how should we
trust our intuition?

00:05:57.820 --> 00:06:00.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I believe that we
must trust our intuition.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:03.380 align:middle line:84%
Intuition is that still
small voice inside of us

00:06:03.380 --> 00:06:06.360 align:middle line:84%
that will tell us the
absolute truth about things.

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:08.180 align:middle line:84%
And usually, in
Western culture, it's

00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:09.960 align:middle line:90%
way beneath the rational mind.

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:11.510 align:middle line:90%
And the mind will be blaring.

00:06:11.510 --> 00:06:13.200 align:middle line:84%
The thoughts, our
hopes, our dreams,

00:06:13.200 --> 00:06:15.410 align:middle line:84%
our laundry list of
things to do, all of that

00:06:15.410 --> 00:06:16.940 align:middle line:90%
is what is usually the loudest.

00:06:16.940 --> 00:06:19.340 align:middle line:84%
But if we learn to
be quiet, we learn

00:06:19.340 --> 00:06:21.350 align:middle line:84%
to go inside of
ourselves, and sense

00:06:21.350 --> 00:06:23.735 align:middle line:84%
this quiet intuitive
voice inside,

00:06:23.735 --> 00:06:25.360 align:middle line:84%
it will tell us the
truth about things.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.870 align:middle line:90%
And I believe that we must.

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:30.210 align:middle line:84%
In order to make truly informed
decisions about our lives,

00:06:30.210 --> 00:06:33.530 align:middle line:84%
we need to trust this intuitive
voice and let it guide us.

00:06:33.530 --> 00:06:36.020 align:middle line:84%
I equate it with our
higher self and I see it

00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:38.545 align:middle line:84%
as a direct extension
with spirituality.

00:06:38.545 --> 00:06:41.975 align:middle line:84%
>> But how do you know it's
just not your crazy imagination?

00:06:41.975 --> 00:06:45.920 align:middle line:84%
>> [LAUGHS] The crazy
imagination doesn't speak

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:46.970 align:middle line:90%
in intuitive terms.

00:06:46.970 --> 00:06:49.850 align:middle line:84%
The most authentic kinds
of intuitions that I found

00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:52.070 align:middle line:84%
comes through either in a
very neutral sense where

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.190 align:middle line:90%
you ask a question.

00:06:53.190 --> 00:06:55.130 align:middle line:84%
Let's say, what
kind of treatment

00:06:55.130 --> 00:06:57.060 align:middle line:84%
should I do for
my health problem?

00:06:57.060 --> 00:06:59.290 align:middle line:84%
What kind of treatment
would feel good in my body?

00:06:59.290 --> 00:07:02.780 align:middle line:84%
And then the intuition comes
in a very neutral sense.

00:07:02.780 --> 00:07:05.435 align:middle line:84%
It's a very informational
sense or else

00:07:05.435 --> 00:07:08.390 align:middle line:84%
it comes through with
a compassionate tone.

00:07:08.390 --> 00:07:11.030 align:middle line:84%
Oftentimes, intuition will come
through with the most beautiful

00:07:11.030 --> 00:07:12.680 align:middle line:90%
sense of compassion behind it.

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:14.900 align:middle line:84%
And whenever there's
a lot of emotion

00:07:14.900 --> 00:07:17.510 align:middle line:84%
with a so-called intuition,
I always question it.

00:07:17.510 --> 00:07:20.370 align:middle line:84%
Whenever an intuition has a
very high emotional charge,

00:07:20.370 --> 00:07:22.370 align:middle line:84%
I will look inside of
myself and say, well, what

00:07:22.370 --> 00:07:24.260 align:middle line:90%
in myself is being activated?

00:07:24.260 --> 00:07:26.390 align:middle line:90%
And I will not trust it as much.

00:07:26.390 --> 00:07:28.530 align:middle line:90%
>> So if it feels impulsive--

00:07:28.530 --> 00:07:29.330 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:07:29.330 --> 00:07:31.145 align:middle line:84%
>> --would you stand
back a little bit?

00:07:31.145 --> 00:07:34.100 align:middle line:84%
>> If it feels impulsive--
but intuitions have a sense

00:07:34.100 --> 00:07:36.950 align:middle line:84%
of rightness also that we
have to really begin to train

00:07:36.950 --> 00:07:40.280 align:middle line:84%
ourselves to trust, it's
a sense of body rightness.

00:07:40.280 --> 00:07:43.280 align:middle line:84%
And when you begin
to develop intuition,

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:45.690 align:middle line:84%
you get a sense of this knowing
or rightness in the body.

00:07:45.690 --> 00:07:48.470 align:middle line:84%
Some people talk about it as
a gut feeling or that sense

00:07:48.470 --> 00:07:50.228 align:middle line:90%
that all is well inside.

00:07:50.228 --> 00:07:52.520 align:middle line:84%
And one thing that I teach
people to do in my workshops

00:07:52.520 --> 00:07:54.200 align:middle line:84%
and in intuitive
healing is to learn

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:56.630 align:middle line:84%
how to really get inside
of themselves what

00:07:56.630 --> 00:07:59.010 align:middle line:84%
an "intuitive yes" feels like
or what an "intuitive no"

00:07:59.010 --> 00:07:59.810 align:middle line:90%
feels like.

00:07:59.810 --> 00:08:00.170 align:middle line:90%
That's how the beginning.

00:08:00.170 --> 00:08:00.780 align:middle line:90%
>> How do you do that?

00:08:00.780 --> 00:08:01.080 align:middle line:90%
>> All right.

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:01.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Tell us.

00:08:01.910 --> 00:08:05.370 align:middle line:84%
>> The way to really do
this is to ask a question.

00:08:05.370 --> 00:08:08.570 align:middle line:84%
Let's say you have a pressing
question about your health.

00:08:08.570 --> 00:08:10.730 align:middle line:84%
What should I do about
this health problem?

00:08:10.730 --> 00:08:12.240 align:middle line:90%
Should I choose chemotherapy?

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.490 align:middle line:90%
Let's say that's the question.

00:08:13.490 --> 00:08:15.470 align:middle line:84%
And just pose in a
yes or no format.

00:08:15.470 --> 00:08:18.080 align:middle line:84%
Then go inside, get
very quiet, and see

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.330 align:middle line:84%
whatever images,
impressions, sights,

00:08:20.330 --> 00:08:24.390 align:middle line:84%
smells, sounds, knowings,
body sensations come to you.

00:08:24.390 --> 00:08:26.660 align:middle line:84%
And then begin to
really evaluate that.

00:08:26.660 --> 00:08:30.900 align:middle line:84%
For me, an intuitive yes feels
like a quickening of energy.

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:32.240 align:middle line:90%
It feels like an excitement.

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.010 align:middle line:84%
It feels like my
body is actually

00:08:34.010 --> 00:08:35.840 align:middle line:90%
pulled towards something.

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:38.450 align:middle line:84%
There's a sense of
energy and enthusiasm.

00:08:38.450 --> 00:08:40.520 align:middle line:84%
Whereas if I tune
in and get a no,

