out of the way so you can get

00:08:54.110 --> 00:08:55.902 align:middle line:90%
in kind of a reading?

00:08:55.902 --> 00:08:57.970 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, what I teach
people to do in the book,

00:08:57.970 --> 00:09:00.470 align:middle line:84%
