underneath the fear.

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:05.450 align:middle line:84%
And this does come
with practice.

00:09:05.450 --> 00:09:07.790 align:middle line:84%
Chemotherapy is a
big issue, but it's

00:09:07.790 --> 00:09:10.010 align:middle line:84%
important to be able
to go inside whatever

00:09:10.010 --> 00:09:11.210 align:middle line:90%
your question is.

00:09:11.210 --> 00:09:12.740 align:middle line:84%
You're asking about
a relationship,

00:09:12.740 --> 00:09:14.660 align:middle line:84%
you're asking
about chemotherapy,

00:09:14.660 --> 00:09:16.160 align:middle line:84%
you're asking about
a career, you're

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:18.410 align:middle line:84%
asking about you have manic
depressive disorder, what

00:09:18.410 --> 00:09:19.290 align:middle line:90%
to do about it?

00:09:19.290 --> 00:09:21.320 align:middle line:90%
Now, these are big questions.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.840 align:middle line:84%
Everybody has big issues
inside of themselves

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:26.240 align:middle line:84%
and what's so important
about intuition is to learn

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:27.807 align:middle line:90%
how to find a neutral place.

00:09:27.807 --> 00:09:29.390 align:middle line:84%
And one thing that
I teach and I think

00:09:29.390 --> 00:09:31.150 align:middle line:84%
that's an essential
skill for everyone

00:09:31.150 --> 00:09:33.560 align:middle line:84%
is to learn how to
breathe, breathe, breathe,

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:35.750 align:middle line:90%
go in and find yes.

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:36.620 align:middle line:90%
Remember to breathe.

00:09:36.620 --> 00:09:38.180 align:middle line:90%
People forget to breathe.

00:09:38.180 --> 00:09:40.490 align:middle line:10%
And to go inside and
find that quiet place

00:09:40.490 --> 00:09:42.680 align:middle line:10%
and ask to have the fear lifted.

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:45.620 align:middle line:10%
When you go in, ask to be
able to find a neutral place

00:09:45.620 --> 00:09:49.230 align:middle line:10%
