very down to Earth.

00:15:23.630 --> 00:15:25.892 align:middle line:90%
Or they can be very metaphoric.

00:15:25.892 --> 00:15:27.350 align:middle line:84%
Learning how to
interpret dreams is

00:15:27.350 --> 00:15:28.808 align:middle line:84%
something I go
through in the book,

00:15:28.808 --> 00:15:30.200 align:middle line:90%
and it's really important.

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:32.450 align:middle line:84%
As a beginner I always
suggest that people go out

00:15:32.450 --> 00:15:34.910 align:middle line:84%
