about dream symbols.

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:40.280 align:middle line:84%
But you have to be very careful
about defining dream symbols

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:42.980 align:middle line:84%
too carefully, because
what could mean something

00:15:42.980 --> 00:15:45.230 align:middle line:84%
to one person would be very
different than another.

00:15:45.230 --> 00:15:46.438 align:middle line:90%
And I'll give you an example.

00:15:46.438 --> 00:15:48.688 align:middle line:84%
There was one period where
I was going through my life

00:15:48.688 --> 00:15:49.970 align:middle line:90%
where nothing was working out.

00:15:49.970 --> 00:15:51.440 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't even get
the plumber to come.

00:15:51.440 --> 00:15:52.190 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't organize.

00:15:52.190 --> 00:15:53.482 align:middle line:90%
Everything was falling through.

00:15:53.482 --> 00:15:55.040 align:middle line:84%
And I was getting
very frustrated

00:15:55.040 --> 00:15:56.850 align:middle line:90%
and I was complaining a lot.

00:15:56.850 --> 00:15:58.340 align:middle line:90%
I was getting very ungrateful.

00:15:58.340 --> 00:16:00.140 align:middle line:84%
About that time, I
had a dream that I

00:16:00.140 --> 00:16:02.080 align:middle line:90%
was diagnosed with leukemia.

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:04.550 align:middle line:84%
And in the dream,
I was so terrified

00:16:04.550 --> 00:16:06.530 align:middle line:84%
that my life was going
to be taken from me.

00:16:06.530 --> 00:16:09.530 align:middle line:84%
And I woke up in the
morning just so relieved

00:16:09.530 --> 00:16:12.230 align:middle line:84%
that this wasn't the
reality in my waking life.

00:16:12.230 --> 00:16:14.480 align:middle line:84%
All right, how did I know
that wasn't a psychic dream?

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:16.880 align:middle line:84%
At that moment, I tuned
in and I asked myself,

00:16:16.880 --> 00:16:18.080 align:middle line:90%
is this my future?

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:20.210 align:middle line:84%
And I went into look and
I got, definitely no.

00:16:20.210 --> 00:16:21.830 align:middle line:84%
What this dream
was, was a wake-up

00:16:21.830 --> 00:16:23.990 align:middle line:84%
call for me to be
grateful about my life.

00:16:23.990 --> 00:16:25.543 align:middle line:84%
And it was the most
compassionate way

00:16:25.543 --> 00:16:27.710 align:middle line:84%
the universe could have
really, and the quickest way

00:16:27.710 --> 00:16:29.210 align:middle line:84%
